Package: weimea
Type: Package
Title: Weighted Mean Analysis
Version: 0.1.14
Date: 2019-03-21
Authors@R: person("Zeleny", "David",
           email = "zeleny.david@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5157-044X"))
Description: Analysing and testing the relationship community-
    weighted mean (wei mea) of species attributes (traits, Ellenberg-type indicator values) and
    sample attributes by methods of CWM approach, including max test (ter Braak et al. 2012) and
    modified permutation test (Zeleny & Schaffers 2012). CWM approach with correlation, linear regression,
    analysis of variance and design based functions available.
LazyData: TRUE
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
